; Regression test for issue #623: equity preserves virtual flag on mixed accounts
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/623
;
; When an account has both real and virtual postings, the equity command
; must emit the virtual entry with parentheses so the output re-imports
; without a balance error.

2024/01/15 Purchase
    Expenses:Food       $50.00
    Assets:Checking    $-50.00
    (Expenses:Food)     $10.00

test equity
2024/01/15 Opening Balances
    Assets:Checking                          $-50.00
    Expenses:Food                             $50.00
    (Expenses:Food)                           $10.00
end test
